libs.content:
find_library(avutil_library
	names
		avutil
		avutil-55
		avutil-56
	paths
		/usr/local/lib
		/usr/pkg/lib/ffmpeg3
		/usr/lib
		/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu
		/usr/lib/aarch64-linux-gnu
		/usr/lib/ffmpeg
		/opt/local/lib
		/sw/lib
		/local/lib
		/mingw/lib
		/local/bin
		/mingw/bin
		/bin
)

find_library(avcodec_library
	names
		avcodec
		avcodec-57
		avcodec-58
	paths
		/usr/local/lib
		/usr/pkg/lib/ffmpeg3
		/usr/lib
		/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu
		/usr/lib/aarch64-linux-gnu
		/opt/local/lib
		/sw/lib
		/local/lib
		/mingw/lib
		/local/bin
		/mingw/bin
		/bin
)

find_library(avformat_library
	names
		avformat
		avformat-57
		avformat-58
	paths
		/usr/local/lib
		/usr/pkg/lib/ffmpeg3
		/usr/lib
		/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu
		/usr/lib/aarch64-linux-gnu
		/usr/lib/ffmpeg
		/opt/local/lib
		/sw/lib
		/local/lib
		/local/bin
		/mingw/bin
		/mingw/lib
		/bin
)

find_library(sdl2_library_temp
  names sdl2
  hints
  $env{sdl2dir}
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  paths
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
  c:/mingw/
)

find_library(sdl2main_library
      names sdl2main
      hints
      $env{sdl2dir}
      path_suffixes lib64 lib
      paths
      /sw
      /opt/local
      /opt/csw
      /opt
      c:/mingw/
    )

find_library(sdlffmpeg_library 
  names sdl_ffmpeg
  hints
  $env{sdlffmpegdir}
  $env{sdldir}
  paths
  ~/library/frameworks
  /library/frameworks
  /usr/local
  /usr
  /sw
  /opt/local
  /opt/csw
  /opt
    path_suffixes lib64 lib
)

find_library(clunk_library
  names
    clunk
  paths
    ${clunk_root}/lib
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    /opt/local/lib
    /sw/lib
    /local/lib
    /mingw/lib
	/local/bin
	/mingw/bin
	/usr/local/lib
)
find_library(ogg_library names ogg)
find_library(vorbis_library names vorbis)
find_library(vorbisfile_library names vorbisfile)
